  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to assess the early outcomes when using the Biomerix Revive™ as
      a tension-free onlay patch, Lichtenstein-style, in patients who are candidates for primary,
      unilateral, open inguinal hernia repair.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
